entries.title_d: The clever pirates have ambushed you. You need to prevail and defeat them!
entries.title: Dantooine system: Blacklight pirates attack!
entries.split_quest_alert: Brother Ezkiel: < Now, gather information from one of the pirate ships. The SpyNet have asked us to try and find out where their leader is. >
entries.complete: Brother Ezkiel: < Great work my friend, you beat the ambush. >
